hotel_data.name: Hyatt Centric Fisherman's Wharf San Francisco
hotel_data.hotel_description: Just 3 minutes’ walk from Fisherman's Wharf, the Hyatt features an on-site restaurant and lounge. A heated outdoor pool and hot tub are offered. Free WiFi and a 47” HDTV are featured in all rooms. The Wardroom features an extensive breakfast menu with a la carte options. Modern, yet rustic decor is featured at Brick & Beam; which serves up cocktails in lounge and bar. Snacks, drinks and toiletries are available at the 24-hour Marketplace daily. Styled in modern décor, a Bluetooth capable media hub and an iPod docking station are featured in all rooms. Spa toiletries are included. A mini refrigerator, a coffee maker and laptop sized safe are also provided in each room at Hyatt Fisherman's Wharf. A 24-hour reception is just one of the many convenient amenities offered at Hyatt Fisherman's Wharf San Francisco. Other services include dry cleaning, currency exchange and concierge. A cash machine is located onsite. Historic street car trolleybuses and the famed cable cars are within 2 minutes’ walk from Hyatt . Sweet treats are available at Ghirardelli Square 5 minutes’ walk. PIER 39 is 10 minutes’ walk away. Golden Gate Bridge is 4 miles away. Other nearby attractions include Alcatraz, North Beach and Union Square.

hotel_data.name: Best Western Plus Bayside Hotel
hotel_data.hotel_description: This bay front Oakland hotel offers Free WiFi and a hot full breakfast. A cable/satellite TV, microwave and small refrigerator are featured in each room at the 100% non-smoking Best Western Plus Bayside Hotel. A private bathroom with soaking tub, glass-enclosed shower, bathrobe and hairdryer is provided. A 24-hour front desk with multilingual staff and business center are available for guest convenience. A fitness center is located on site. The Oakland-Alameda County Coliseum and Oakland Arena are 5 miles away. Oakland International Airport is 8 miles away. Union Square in San Francisco is 13 miles away.

hotel_data.name: Hyatt Place San Francisco/Downtown
hotel_data.hotel_description: Offering air-conditioned rooms in the South of Market (SOMA) district of San Francisco, Hyatt Place San Francisco/Downtown is 600 metres from Oracle Park. This 3-star hotel offers a 24-hour front desk and a business centre. Free WiFi is available and private parking can be arranged at an extra charge. At the hotel, every room is equipped with a desk, a flat-screen TV and a private bathroom. All units will provide guests with a fridge. Moscone Center is 1.1 km from Hyatt Place San Francisco/Downtown, while Union Square is 1.7 km away. The nearest airport is San Francisco International Airport, 21 km from the accommodation.
